{"tid":2415289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"漠視爭議 WhatsApp將用戶私隱送fb","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T06:48:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f87b778d12ea32e6acb1d34146e50e49730fd0b","tid":2415289,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/N5DIIIAM2JAKVHMW5V4PAYQV7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FN5DIIIAM2JAKVHMW5V4PAYQV7Q%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=ec000748\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2FN5DIIIAM2JAKVHMW5V4PAYQV7Q%2F&h=b3a360ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/N5DIIIAM2JAKVHMW5V4PAYQV7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n漠視爭議 WhatsApp將用戶私隱送fb<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2TY7srzw_rWAvqE3-Sh1SsZxhKY=/1688x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EAU6LCMZBRGDRJUZCWBRY64TRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2TY7srzw_rWAvqE3-Sh1SsZxhKY%3D%2F1688x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEAU6LCMZBRGDRJUZCWBRY64TRQ.jpg&h=a25bf61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時通訊軟件WhatsApp（圖）早前單方面更新私隱政策，宣佈會跟母公司facebook分享用戶資料，引來極大爭議，更觸發社交移民潮。惟WhatsApp前日指會繼續推行有關政策。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月WhatsApp通知用戶準備更新私隱政策，表示會與fb及其他公司分享用戶數據，包括其電話號碼及位置，原定於本月強制實施，即用戶如要繼續使用程式就必須接受條款更新。全球大量用戶深感不滿，紛紛轉用其他加密訊息應用程式如Telegram和Signal。在全球最多WhatsApp用戶的印度，科技部要求撤回有關更新，fb行政人員更被國會質詢為何要作出相關政策改變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始提醒更新<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。惟WhatsApp前日指會開始提醒用戶檢視和接受更新條款以繼續使用，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"}]}